{"article_id":"E9cVHdIYJyq3PSif","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Special Counsel Robert Mueller ' s office is not staying silent","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"following explosive accusations by a lawyer for President Donald Trump ' s transition team","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"that the investigators","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"looking into claims of collusion with Moscow during the campaign","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"unlawfully received tens of thousands of emails from the General Services Administration .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"Kory Langhofer , the attorney for the Trump for America transition team , sent a seven-page letter to the Senate Homeland Security Committee and the House Oversight Committee ,","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"claiming","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"that employees of the GSA \" unlawfully produced TFA ' s private materials ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"including privileged communications ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"to the special counsel ' s office. \"","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"The GSA ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"which holds all the transition documents ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"handed over the requested \" copies of the emails , laptops , cell phones , and other materials \" of 13 members of the transition team","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"even though the agency \" did not own or control the records in question. \"","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"Langhofer claimed","depth":4},{"id":15,"text":"that they were never informed that the documents were handed over","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"and there were potential violations of attorney-client privilege as well as the Fourth Amendment ,","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"which protects against unlawful search and seizure .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"Axios ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"which broke the news of the emails ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"explains","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"why the communications matter :","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"The transition emails are said to include sensitive exchanges on matters such as potential appointments , gossip about the views of particular senators","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"involved in the confirmation process , speculation about vulnerabilities of Trump nominees , strategizing about press statements , and policy planning on everything from war to taxes .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"A source tells Axios","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"that the transition team will be sending a letter to Mueller","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"asking for some emails to be returned","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"because they ' re privileged .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"\" What they did is totally illegal ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"and they need to fix it , \"","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"the source said .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"But Mueller ' s team begs to differ .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"\" When we have obtained emails in the course of our ongoing criminal investigation ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"we have secured either the account owner ' s consent or appropriate criminal process , \"","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Mueller spokesman Peter Carr said .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Mueller ' s spokesman isn ' t the only one","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"pushing back .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"GSA Deputy Counsel Lenny Loewentritt also contradicted the claims","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"made by Trump ' s transition team .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Loewentritt specifically rejected a claim by the transition lawyer","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"that the late GSA general counsel made a commitment","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"to inform Trump ' s team","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"if there were specific requests for any documents","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"because the campaign \" owned and controlled \" emails","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"that were sent at the time .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"In an interview with BuzzFeed , Lowentritt said","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"that the truth is the exact opposite","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"because the transition team was clearly told that","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"\" in using our devices ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"\" materials \" would not be held back in any law enforcement \" actions .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Former federal prosecutor Renato Mariotti took to Twitter","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"to explain","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"why Trump ' s transition team is \" playing politics \"","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"but the issue itself \" is a bad sign for them. \"","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"For Mariotti , what is unusual in this case is that Mueller ' s team got the emails from the GSA rather than the Trump transition .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"That suggest","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"\" Mueller was concerned","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"that he wouldn ' t receive all of the emails","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"if he obtained them from the Trump team , \"","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"Mariotti writes .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"\" That ' s surprising","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"and suggests","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"that he has reason","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"to distrust Trump ' s team. \"","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"Besides Mariotti makes clear","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"that \" disputes over privilege are common","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"when prosecutors obtain emails and documents from third parties . \"","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"THREAD :","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Why are Trump ' s lawyers upset","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"that Mueller obtained transition emails from a government agency ?","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"( Hint :","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"They ' re just playing politics ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"but this is a bad sign for them . )","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"- Renato Mariotti","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"( @ renato_mariotti )","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"December 16 , 2017","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"9/ One reason comes to mind .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"Mueller was concerned","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"that he wouldn ' t receive all of the emails","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"if he obtained them from the Trump team .","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"That ' s surprising","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"and suggests","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"that he has reason","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"to distrust Trump ' s team .","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"- Renato Mariotti","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"( @ renato_mariotti )","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"December 16 , 2017","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"The privilege claims though could have been easily resolved with a letter to Mueller rather than Congress ,","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"Mariotti writes ,","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"noting","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"that ' s the biggest hint","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"that the ultimate goal is to taint the investigation .","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"\" The biggest conclusion","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"I ' d draw from their letter","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"is that they ' re concerned about Mueller ' s investigation","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"and are doing whatever they can","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"to discredit it , \"","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"Mariotti writes .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"\" Their claims themselves are weak","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"and are meant to persuade people","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"who know nothing about criminal investigations . \"","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"19/ The biggest conclusion","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"I ' d draw from their letter","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"is that they ' re concerned about Mueller ' s investigation","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"and are doing whatever they can","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"to discredit it .","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"Their claims themselves are weak","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"and are meant to persuade people","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"who know nothing about criminal investigations . /end","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"- Renato Mariotti","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"( @ renato_mariotti )","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"December 16 , 2017","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"Rep. Eric Swalwell also went on Twitter","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"to dismiss the supposed complaints by the transition team as much ado about nothing .","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"\" ' Private documents ' on a U.S. Government , public email system ?","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"What are they afraid was found ?","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"Baloney .","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"This is another attempt","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"to discredit Mueller","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"as his # TrumpRussia probe tightens , \"","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"he wrote on Twitter .","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"\" Private documents \" on a US Government , public email system ?","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"What are they afraid","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"was found ?","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"Baloney .","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"This is another attempt","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"to discredit Mueller","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"as his # TrumpRussia probe tightens .","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"https : //t.co/VZTkwiGmoB...","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"https : //t.co/q0HTbwpQRK","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"- Rep. Eric Swalwell","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"( @ RepSwalwell )","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"December 16 , 2017","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":265,"left":137,"right":264,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":0,"right":136,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":1,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":134,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":134,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":149,"right":263,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":145,"right":148,"relation